values:
I'm Charmion, and this has become my fiction journal. Expect to find slash here, so if that's not your cup of tea, feel free to move on. At the moment I'm writing in Tolkien's wonderful universe again, more specifically Second Age Elrond/Gil-galad. Other fandoms I like and follow are Ellen Kushner's <i>Swordspoint</i> universe, good old <i>Velvet Goldmine</i> and everything Libertines. It's kinda ecclectic, I know. 

I adore comments, but don't feel obliged to leave any. Though if you know any good fic in above mentioned fandoms... I'm always up for recommendations and will be eternally* grateful.


<font size="-2">*I'm aware that in internet time this is probably two weeks, but still!</font>

